movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Neat movie - Fun and entertaining
review: Not as earth shattering as Episode IV, but still lots of fun. The pod race scene was amazing. The lightsaber duel between obi-wan kenobi, qui-gon jinn, and darth maul was one of the best cinematic style sword fights to be found. (Though, alas, not as good as princess bride)
